'''izeffaren ikaṛbuksilinen''' d [[azeffar agman|izeffaren igmanen]] yellan deg usismel n [[Tagrawt n ukaṛbuksil|tegrawt n ukaṛbuksil]] tamesɣant (COOH), Yettak-d i weprutun taftart-is tamatant R-, d [[asemselsay]] ya d aẓaṛ [[Alkyl|alkylan]] neɣ d abelkim n [[hidṛujin|uhidṛujin]], Dɣa yettili s waṭas deg [[agama|ugama]]

== Iglamen isengamen ==
* Izeffaren ikaṛbuksilinen d [[tizzugla (takrura)|uddisen imzzugliyen]], s wakka zemren ad gen (ad xedmen) [[turza tahidṛujint]] gar n [[acubar|icubar]]
* Deg tseddarin yeflalen (iɛlayen) n wezɣal izeffaren ikaṛbuksilinen ttilin deg talɣa n uddis imisin n [[taftart takrurant|teftart tacubrant]]
